This repository contains data processing pipeline for "10xDevs" course. We're working on HTML files that are pulled directly from external platform, that contain all the typical elements - headers, paragraphs, images, iframes, etc.

The goal is to process these HTML files and split them into smaller chunks, that can be used in RAG pipeline.

## Project Structure

* `data/source` - contains raw HTML files that are pulled directly from external platform
* `data/chunks` - contains cleaned up HTML files that are ready to be used in the RAG pipeline
* `src/pipeline.ts` - main pipeline file that contains the logic for processing the HTML files and splitting them into smaller chunks (used Tech Stack listed below)
* `src/strategies/*.ts` - contains different strategies for processing the HTML files and splitting them into smaller chunks
* `src/helpers/*.ts` - contains helper functions for the pipeline (data cleanup, tag conversions, etc.)
* `src/types.ts` - contains TypeScript types for core parts of the pipeline

## Tech Stack

* Node 22
* TypeScript 5
